title: January T-Mobile updates
content:
Sorry, added onto another existing thread...

Received T-Mobile TA notification for update for the 4XL on 01/15/2020. Saying newest acceptable version for this model for T-Mobile is -  QQ1B.200205.002.

https://developers.google.com/android/ota shows the following as being available -
10.0.0 (QQ1B.200105.004, Jan 2020)    
10.0.0 (QQ1C.200105.004, Jan 2020, TW & JP)
10.0.0 (QQ1D.200105.002, Jan 2020, NTT DOCOMO)

Looks like it went from QQ1B.200105.XXX to QQ1D.200105.XXX (from QQ1B to QQ1D). Where is QQ1B.200.205.XXX per the T-Mobile TA?

Any help is appreciated.
